Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{It was a penguin, right?}{\i1}Là chim cánh cụt, phải không?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. A purple penguin.}Ừ, một con chim cánh cụt màu tím.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{There are two of them? [9 frames]}Có hai chiếc ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wait a minute, it might be\Na real courier service.}Đợi chút.\NCó thể là một dịch vụ giao hàng thực sự.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's a matter of how to\Nfigure out if they are legit...}Làm sao ta biết được liệu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.52,Main,split,0,0,0,,{That's easy.}Đơn giản thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.92,Main,split,0,0,0,,{We fire a shot, and the one\Nthat runs is the one we want.}Cứ bắn một phát, \Nnếu chúng bỏ chạy thì là tội phạm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is the first time\NI agree with you on something. [10 frames]}Lần đầu tiên tôi đồng ý với cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{Y-You guys!}Mọi người!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{What are you gonna do\Nif they're both real?!}Nếu cả hai đều là bọn tội phạm thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They both ran?}{\i0}{\i1}Cả hai đều bỏ trốn?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We didn't consider that option...}{\i0}{\i1}Ta đã không tính đến trường hợp đó.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.48,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I'm trusting you with that one! [snapped to start keyframe to lower CPS]}Cô xử lý tên đó đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.19,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I have to pay them back for yesterday, too.}Tôi phải trả món nợ hôm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:22.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{Forgive us!}Chúng tôi xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{W-We'll pay the parking fee!}Chúng tôi sẽ trả phí đỗ xe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{This way?!}Chúng kia rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Spike! Draw them out!}{\i0}{\i1}Spike. Lôi chúng ra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{let the virus go in there!}{\i0}{\i1}Sẽ rất lộn xộn nếu chúng thả virus vào đó.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I know!}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi biết rồi.{\i0}
Comment: 1,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.13,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,{\i1}Đã 31 cú đánh mà vẫn không trúng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{So, let's see what ya got...}Để xem các ngươi có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.48,Main,split,0,0,0,,{He's here.}Hắn kia rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:51.83,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Waste of time.}Hắn chỉ phí thời gian thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.76,Main,split,0,0,0,,{He's after the arm...}Hắn nhắm vào cánh tay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.71,Main,split,0,0,0,,{He's not taking us seriously! Ruth!}Hắn đánh giá thấp ta quá, Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ready to go anytime. [9 frames]}Sẵn sàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Take that!}{\i1}Đỡ này!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{Welcome... [9 frames]}Chào mừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{Excellent!}Nhào vô!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Bingo!}Nhắm được rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{He's holding up pretty well. [snap to start keyframe to lower CPS? Extra lead-in at least]}Hắn cố chống trả.
